sourcemode boxvolume

parameters 0.1	0.1	0.5	0.5		0.01	0.01

particle neutron

ActiveTime 0
PhaseSpaceWeighting 0

Emin 10e-9
Emax 150e-9
spectrum 1

phi_v_min 0
phi_v_max 0
phi_v 1

theta_v_min 5
theta_v_max 5
theta_v 1

